    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Historical Event\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze a historical image alongside a primary source PDF.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Upload one of the **historical images** from the Library. **Copy and paste** the following prompt:\r\n\r\n> Analyze this image. What does the image reveal about this historical event? \r\n\r\n2. Upload the **image** again and the **matching primary source PDF** from the Library. **Modify** the following prompt and press **Send**:\r\n\r\n> Analyze this image and document together. What do they reveal about this historical event?\r\n\r\n3. Read AI Chat's response.\r\n4. Modify your prompt to have AI generate different outputs. Compare the responses. Some prompt ideas:\r\n    - Ask AI to generate a newspaper headline based on the image alone\r\n    - Ask AI to generate a radio broadcast as if the event is happening live\r\n    - Ask AI to generate a movie synopsis based on the image and PDF\r\n   \r\n---\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-file-image-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I upload an image?**]\r\n- Click the button labeled **Upload** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Library**\r\n- Then browse the existing images.\r\n- When you have an image to upload, click the checkbox next to it to select it and then click **Open**.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::",
